5#ifndef V8_COMPILER_TURBOSHAFT_REDUCER_TRAITS_H_
6#define V8_COMPILER_TURBOSHAFT_REDUCER_TRAITS_H_

8#include <type_traits>
9
10namespace v8::internal::compiler::turboshaft {
11
12template <class Assembler, bool has_gvn, template <class> class... Reducers>
13class ReducerStack;
14
15template <typename Next>
16class GenericReducerBase;
17template <typename Next>
18class EmitProjectionReducer;
19template <typename Next>
20class TSReducerBase;
21
22// is_same_reducer compares two reducers.
23template <template <typename> typename T, template <typename> typename U>
24struct is_same_reducer : public std::bool_constant<false> {};
25
26template <template <typename> typename Reducer>
27struct is_same_reducer<Reducer, Reducer> : public std::bool_constant<true> {};
28
29template <template <typename> typename...>
30struct reducer_list {};
31// Converts a ReducerStack {Next} to a reducer_list<>;
32template <typename Next>
33struct reducer_stack_to_list;
34template <typename A, bool has_gvn, template <typename> typename... Reducers>
35struct reducer_stack_to_list<ReducerStack<A, has_gvn, Reducers...>> {
36 using type = reducer_list<Reducers...>;
37};
38
39// Checks if a reducer_list<> {RL} contains reducer {R}.
40template <typename RL, template <typename> typename R>
41struct reducer_list_contains;
42template <template <typename> typename R, template <typename> typename Head,
43 template <typename> typename... Tail>
44struct reducer_list_contains<reducer_list<Head, Tail...>, R> {
45 static constexpr bool value =
46 is_same_reducer<Head, R>::value ||
47 reducer_list_contains<reducer_list<Tail...>, R>::value;
48};
49template <template <typename> typename R>
50struct reducer_list_contains<reducer_list<>, R>
51 : public std::bool_constant<false> {};
52
53// Checks if a reducer_list<> {RL} starts with reducer {R}.
54template <typename RL, template <typename> typename R>
55struct reducer_list_starts_with;
56template <template <typename> typename R, template <typename> typename Head,
57 template <typename> typename... Tail>
58struct reducer_list_starts_with<reducer_list<Head, Tail...>, R>
59 : public std::bool_constant<is_same_reducer<Head, R>::value> {};
60template <template <typename> typename R>
61struct reducer_list_starts_with<reducer_list<>, R>
62 : public std::bool_constant<false> {};
63
64// Check if the {Next} ReducerStack contains {Reducer}.
65template <typename Next, template <typename> typename Reducer>
66struct next_contains_reducer {
67 using list = typename reducer_stack_to_list<Next>::type;
68 static constexpr bool value = reducer_list_contains<list, Reducer>::value;
69};
70
71// Check if in the {Next} ReducerStack, any of {Reducer} comes next.
72template <typename Next, template <typename> typename... Reducer>
73struct next_reducer_is {
74 using list = typename reducer_stack_to_list<Next>::type;
75 static constexpr bool value =
76 (reducer_list_starts_with<list, Reducer>::value || ...);
77};
78
79// TODO(dmercadier): EmitProjectionReducer is not always the bottom of the stack
80// because it could be succeeded by a ValueNumberingReducer. We should take this
81// into account in next_is_bottom_of_assembler_stack.
82template <typename Next>
83struct next_is_bottom_of_assembler_stack
84 : public next_reducer_is<Next, GenericReducerBase, EmitProjectionReducer,
85 TSReducerBase> {};
86
